_sText:
De_elysion is a port of the De_elysion map from the CSGO game.

Also, additional map optimization has been done.

De_elysion took 7th place on the 2020 wingman mapping contest.

Original map description:

Terrorists have infiltrated Elysion on the 39th floor and are ready to plant explosives in the main hall where the building is the weakest. Everybody has already evacuated the building and it is up to the security force to stop the terrorists at all cost.
